1. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture): The paper discusses the deployment of NB-IoT technology over cellular networks, which falls under the domain of networking and internet architecture. 

2. cs.IT (Information Theory): The paper may involve information theory concepts related to the transmission and reception of data over cellular networks. 

3. cs.COMM (Communications and Networking): The paper discusses the deployment of small cell NB-IoT, which is a communication and networking technology. 

4. cs.AR (Hardware Architecture): The paper may involve hardware architecture aspects related to the design and implementation of NB-IoT systems. 

5. cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems): The paper may involve multi-agent systems concepts related to the coordination and management of small cell NB-IoT deployment.
